        <Parent_String>visual and representational concepts [300056326], formal concepts (artistic concept) [300164603], artistic concepts [300168394], concepts in the arts and humanities [300056107], Associated Concepts (hierarchy name) [300055126], Associated Concepts Facet [300264086]</Parent_String>
